    "description": "<div><p>Clad in tattered robes that once boasted intricate patterns and symbols of a bygone era, these undead spellcasters wield an aura of malevolence and ancient knowledge. Vaelorian Magi command the forces of death and decay, having transitioned from live necromancers to undead beings long ago. Their skeletal hands, often the only thing visible under their robes, bear the mark of countless rituals and forbidden spells, remnants of a life devoted to unlocking the secrets of forbidden knowledge.</p></div>",
